   770→## Who's using dotenv?
   772→[These npm modules depend on it.](https://www.npmjs.com/browse/depended/dotenv)
   773→
   774→Projects that expand it often use the [keyword "dotenv" on npm](https://www.npmjs.com/search?q=keywords:dotenv).
